---
By: John Powell
Locus:
  Page: 219
  Verse: 18
Tags:
  - Habits
---
It is very important to realize that we are creatures of habit. Every time
we think a certain way, seek a certain good, use a given motive, a habit is
forming and deepening in us. Like a groove that is being furrowed, each
repetition adds a new depth to the habit.
